【Лебединое озеро】
"For darkness I feared...I just want to be perfect." - Black Swan (2010)
Shooting swan lake eli was definitely something I felt nostalgic about because ballet used to be a HUGE part of my life since childhood. It felt...unreal putting on those pointe shoes again, felt like 6 years ago i was still in the dance room with my friends having lessons and preparing for pointe exams.
Thanks again yet to the LEGENDARY pireze to make this happen. One week back from Fiji with those tan lines was a bit nerve-racking for me because the tutu was too beautiful to ruin by tan lines on my back ;w;
But then it turned on EXTREMELY WELL!!
Again, sorry for the belated uploads and updates...Life has been--well, busy and i hope you guys will still be here and support me!! Once again, thank you for staying with me!!
